                                    PRESENTS
NUMBER:  --
NAME:    KLONDIKE III HD FIX
DETAILS: LETS YOU PLAY CARDS FROM ANYWHERE!
RELEASE: 10-NOV-95.
UPDATED: 29-JAN-97. (Happy birthday to me!) :-)


@{"INTRO TEXT" link "INTRO_TEXT"}
